stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> Preprocessing : pre_process POST
    Preprocessing --> Detecting : predict_images
    Detecting --> Converting : convert_to_image
    Converting --> Segmenting : segment_image
    Segmenting --> Calculating : selected statistics
    Segmenting --> Completed : no statistics selected
    Calculating --> Completed

    Preprocessing --> Cancelling : cancel_progress
    Detecting --> Cancelling : cancel_progress
    Converting --> Cancelling : cancel_progress
    Segmenting --> Cancelling : cancel_progress
    Calculating --> Cancelling : cancel_progress
    Idle --> Cancelled : cancel before work starts
    Cancelling --> Cancelled : delete runs and clear session state

    note right of Preprocessing
      Progress phases are written to
      media/progress/sha256.json
    end note

    note right of Cancelling
      Cancel requests also create
      media/progress/sha256.cancel
    end note

    Completed --> [*]
    Cancelled --> [*]
